name: Bestseller among Russians
description:
I. The main value of art is its caloric content. The more harmful the content, the more interesting it is.
II. Public disapproval of unwanted content is a flavor enhancer (ingredient) that increases interest in it.
III. The ingredients used in the creation of art are familiar and recognizable to the consumer. Cooked with soul.
IV. The composition contains a "fatty" style that causes the consumer's appetite for the content of the product, through which the taste and its main essence are revealed.
V. The composition is not important. Only the taste invested by the author and the taste perception of the consumer are important.
